{"tid":1795662,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"藍問： 練武之人，遇到不公義既事就要企出黎，武之初心。","createTime":"2019-12-24T05:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T06:17:56.000Z","uid":6181,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ed3261f9262a37cb121a06e0965dfd337aab703","tid":1795662,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLyYKAw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLyYKAw.jpg&h=f9e7de08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"036423a61c5de4d726719517009bc40548add779","tid":1795662,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OzEkXV1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOzEkXV1.jpg&h=fbe19142&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01870c7c3d91af8fd33ff4376c9c02ab71cae20d","tid":1795662,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fHq0XWa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfHq0XWa.png&h=8c86f63e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"650149c2f59e98854e049fb882ed20afcf924383","tid":1795662,"uid":266100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:43:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b183f35536c97ddefd7be7c5d5af4a007aee75b","tid":1795662,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去大半年，大家既生活都過得好壓抑，好似見到有希望但係又唔知前路候點。有人或者係依大半年同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手離婚，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸又或者有家歸不得，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=26fdb89e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}